Class Particle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Particle

  • public class Particle
extends java.lang.Object
    Particle is used to draw shapes and some apply to visual effects, and was blend color overlapping objects and animation objects.
    Author:
    Yuxing HU, Xiaorong HE
    See Also:
    GraphicsContext, Color, Paint

      • Particle

        public Particle​(double posX,
                double posY,
                double velX,
                double velY,
                double targetX,
                double targetY,
                javafx.scene.paint.Paint color,
                int size,
                boolean usePhysics,
                boolean hasTail)
        Particle class is used to initialize the origin firework spark particle.
        Parameters:
        posX - Initial position of value x
        posY - Initial position of value y
        velX - An update parameter of x
        velY - An update parameter of y
        targetX - New position of particle x
        targetY - New position of particle y
        color - The particle's color
        size - The size of particle
        usePhysics - Boolean instance to determine whether to implement gravity of article
        hasTail - Boolean instance to determine whether to implement tail of particle.
